" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Macklemore-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Macklemore-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Macklemore-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Macklemore-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Macklemore-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Macklemore-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Macklemore">Macklemore</a>发行了他的新抗议歌曲“ Hucked Up”，针对以色列，<a href="/artists/Donald-Trump">唐纳德·特朗普</a>和<a href="/artists/Elon-Musk">埃隆·马斯克</a>。</p><p>这首歌看到了音乐家 - 真实姓名本杰明·哈格蒂（Benjamin Haggerty） - 说唱<em>“世界着火了，我们没有拥有几美元的水 /囚犯，You All / New Era Ushered，但White -Premace仍在负责 / Talkin中“从白宫草坪上殖民加沙”，</em>指的是毁灭性的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/la-wildfires-more-than-1000-music-professionals-supported-by-charity-musicares-3828869">洛杉矶野火</a>，以及特朗普的总统职位以及他为美国拥有加沙地带所有权的计划。</p><p> Macklemore继续在合唱中打电话给Musk，说：“他们让我搞砸了（Woo，Woo） /和Elon，我们确切地知道那是什么，Bruh，”指的是Tech亿万富翁<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/elon-musk-sparks-backlash-with-nazi-like-gesture-at-trump-inauguration-3830625">，在唐纳德期间做出两个纳粹般的手势特朗普的总统就职典礼</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Macklemore-搞砸了（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sn9EKC9nqU4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这首歌还针对科技公司和首席执行官，亿万富翁，媒体审查制度等，但突出了抵抗力量的力量。</p><p>曲目的最后一节经文看到说唱歌手在接下来的几年里与特朗普在白宫和<em>说唱集中往来</em>：<em>没有说关于种族灭绝 /知道你的孙子的狗屎会问你，“为什么？”。</em></p><p>由奥马尔·阿拉利（Omar Alali）执导的“他妈的UP的随附音乐视频都以著名的社会主义者Eugene V. Debs的名字打开，上面写着：“所有语言中最英勇的报价都是&#39;革命&#39;。在美国发生的各种问题的片段。</p><p> “搞砸了”跟随“ Hind&#39;s Hall”和“ Hind&#39;s Hall 2”，这是一对Pro-Palestine歌曲Macklemore去年发行的。所有由“搞砸”赚取的收益都将捐给联合国代理商<a href="https://www.unrwausa.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">UNRWA USA</a> ，这为巴勒斯坦难民提供了缓解。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DBbpCXgPfPw/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115