9点开始销售，现在预售的选项现已直播。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fkendrick-lamar-tickets%2Fartist%2F1480454" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处购买门票</a>，并找到下面的旅行日期清单。</p><h2><strong>肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）和SZA的英国和欧洲巡演日期是：</strong></h2><p><strong>七月</strong><br /><strong>2  - 德国科隆 @ Rheinenergiestadion</strong><br /> <strong>4  - 德国法兰克福 @ Deutsche Bank Park</strong><br /> <strong>8  - 英国格拉斯哥 @汉普顿公园</strong><br /><strong>10  - 英国伯明翰 @ Villa Park</strong><br /> <strong>13  - 荷兰阿姆斯特丹@Johan Cruijff竞技场</strong><br /><strong>15  - 法国巴黎 @ Paris ladéfense竞技场</strong><br /><strong>16  - 法国巴黎 @ Paris ladéfense竞技场[新]</strong><br /> <strong>19  - 英国加的夫 @公国体育场</strong><br /><strong>22  - 英国伦敦 @托特纳姆热刺体育场</strong><br /><strong>23  - 英国伦敦 @托特纳姆热刺体育场[新]</strong><br /> <strong>27  - 里斯本，葡萄牙 @ estadio do restelo</strong><br /> <strong>30  - 巴塞罗那，西班牙 @ estadiolímpicLluís公司</strong></p><p><strong>八月</strong><br /><strong>2  - 罗马，意大利 @ STADIO OLIMPICO</strong><br /> <strong>6  - 华沙​​，波兰 @ pge narodowy</strong><br /> <strong>9  - 斯德哥尔摩，瑞典 @ 3arena</strong></p><p>据报道，本周早些时候，拉马尔在超级碗Lix半场表演中的插槽持续了13350万现场观众，以及在YouTube上的380万次观看次数， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamars-super-bowl-performance-is-now-the-most-watched-halftime-show-ever-3837220">这是历史上最受欢迎的超级碗表演</a>。</p><p>这也是在说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2025-see-the-full-list-of-winners-3833854">在2025年格莱美奖上获得五个奖项</a>之后不久，其中包括年度最佳唱片和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-on-the-deeper-meaning-of-not-like-us-it-is-the-type-of-man-i-represent-3804972">他的Drake Diss歌曲“ Not Like Us”</a>的年度最佳歌曲。然后，在他在演奏期间打破了这首歌之后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamars-not-like-us-streams-jump-by-430-per-cent-after-super-bowl-performance-3836793">确认赛道上的溪流上升了430％。</a> </p><figure id="attachment_3836667" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3836667" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3836667" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-sza@2000x1270.jpg" alt="肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）和SZA在超级碗2025演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-sza@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-sza@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-sza@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-sza@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-sza@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-sza@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3836667" class="wp-caption-text">肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）和SZA在2025年超级碗上表演。</figcaption></figure><p>为了表演，肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）也加入了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/samuel-l-jackson">塞缪尔·杰克逊（Samuel L. Jackson）</a>和塞雷娜·威廉姆斯（Serena Williams）。</p><p>新节目还遵循了他的最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kendrick-lamar-gnx-review-3815647">《 GNX》（GNX）</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-surprise-releases-brand-new-album-gnx-listen-in-full-3815187">的惊喜释放</a>，去年11月， <em>NME</em>获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kendrick-lamar-gnx-review-3815647">五星级的发光评论</a>。</p><p>对于SZA，日期是<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/sza-live-at-glastonbury-2024-setlist-review-photos-3770784">在格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）2024年的巨大标题插槽</a>之后，紧随她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sza-confirms-sos-deluxe-lana-will-release-this-week-3822809">发行的“ lana”的</a>高跟鞋， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sza-confirms-new-album-lana-is-deluxe-edition-of-sos-the-clock-starts-now-3820629">这是她2022年LP“ SOS”的豪华版本</a>，该版本在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sza-announces-sos-deluxe-edition-titled-lana-3495755">大约一年的猜测发布</a>后于12月到达。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-sza-add-extra-london-and-paris-shows-grand-national-2025-tour-3837815">肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）和SZA邮报（Sza）在2025年的“大国”（Grand National）体育馆巡回演出中添加了额外的伦敦和巴黎表演，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
泰勒·劳特纳（Taylor Lautner https://www.nme.com/news/tv/taylor-lautner-confirms-meta-twilight-inspired-spin-off-3837807?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=taylor-lautner-confirms-meta-twilight-inspired-分拆Victoria LuxfordThu, 13 Feb 2025 16:59:02 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV NewsUncategorised https://www.nme.com/?p=3837807 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Taylor-Lautner-Premiere.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="泰勒·劳特纳（Taylor Lautner）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Taylor-Lautner-Premiere.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Taylor-Lautner-Premiere-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Taylor-Lautner-Premiere-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Taylor-Lautner-Premiere-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Taylor-Lautner-Premiere-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Taylor-Lautner-Premiere-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “就在我以为我出去的时候……他们把我拉回去了”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/taylor-lautner-confirms-meta-twilight-inspired-spin-off-3837807">泰勒·劳特纳（Taylor Lautner）的帖子证实了元&#39;暮光之城启发的衍生产品，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Taylor-Lautner-Premiere.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="泰勒·劳特纳（Taylor Lautner）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Taylor-Lautner-Premiere.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Taylor-Lautner-Premiere-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Taylor-Lautner-Premiere-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Taylor-Lautner-Premiere-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Taylor-Lautner-Premiere-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Taylor-Lautner-Premiere-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>前<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/twilight"><em>暮光之</em></a>星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-lautner">泰勒·劳特纳（Taylor Lautner）</a>在一个名为<em>泰勒·劳特纳（Taylor Lautner）的新节目中拥抱他的过去：狼人猎人</em>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/robert-pattinson-on-twilight-trolls-james-dean-and-moving-on-from-teen-stardom-nme-cover-feature-757067"><em>罗伯特</em>·帕丁森（Robert Pattinson）</a></li></ul><p>脚本节目将看到一个虚构的劳特纳（Lautner）的虚构版本，既是好莱坞演员又是狼人猎人秘密协会的成员。 <a href="https://variety.com/2025/tv/news/taylor-lautner-werewolf-hunter-tv-series-amazon-mgm-studios-1236305182/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>综艺</em></a>报道，该节目正在亚马逊米高梅工作室开发。</p><p>劳特纳（Lautner）对Instagram上的新闻做出了回应，并在标题中发布了报告的屏幕截图，“就在我以为我出去……他们把我拉回去时”。劳特纳（Lautner）在2008年至2012年的<em>《暮光》</em>电影中饰演狼人雅各布·布莱克（Jacob Black）。</p><p>该节目的官方摘要写道：“在最后一部<em>暮光之城</em>电影结束后，泰勒·劳特纳（Taylor Lautner）从聚光灯下消失了。粉丝们推测，小报理论上 - 但事实比小说荒谬。泰勒不仅要度过心理健康。他正在为自己的真正呼唤做准备……泰勒·劳特纳（Taylor Lautner）：狼人猎人”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DF_GbINTtKG/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-